.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
A tiny (~50 lines) script for creating websites with \f[C]pandoc\f[].
.PP
The program paths (#paths) can be set by the following sequence:
.IP "1." 3
Using the per\-project configuration file, \f[I]\&./.ssgrc\f[]
.IP "2." 3
Using the per\-user configuration file, \f[I]~/.ssg\f[]
.SS Options
.TP
.B \-b, \-\-build
Builds site
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B \-d, \-\-dev
Builds site, starts http server (\f[C]httpwatcher\f[]) and watch daemon
(\f[C]entr\f[])
.RS
.RE
.TP
.B [default]
Prints message.
.RS
.RE
